text: "Youngblood" is a song by the pop rock band 5 Seconds of Summer. It was written by Calum Hood, Ali Tamposi, Andrew Watt, Ashton Irwin, and Luke Hemmings. Andrew Watt and Louis Bell helped make it. The song was put out by Capitol Records on 12 April 2018. It was the second single from the bandâ€™s third album, which was also called Youngblood.
